ot work, confined space entry, electrical work, and maintenance activities.',NULL,NULL,'Permits required for: hot work, confined space entry, electrical work, working at height, isolation work. Process: application, risk assessment, authorization, work execution, permit closure. Ensures: safe work practices, proper controls, authorization.','2025-11-24 21:08:24','2025-12-08 18:11:14',NULL,NULL,356,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(288,'step',NULL,'Active','Permit Application and Risk Assessment','Application for permit-to-work including work description, risk assessment, and control measures.',NULL,NULL,'Apply: work description, location, duration, personnel, hazards identified, control measures. Assess: risks, required controls, isolation requirements, emergency procedures. Document: permit application, risk assessment.','2025-11-24 21:08:24','2025-11-24 21:08:24',NULL,NULL,287,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(289,'step',NULL,'Active','Permit Authorization','Authorization of permit-to-work by authorized person after verification of controls and conditions.',NULL,NULL,'Authorize: verify risk assessment, verify controls in place, verify isolations, verify personnel trained, sign permit. Authorized by: competent person, EHS, area supervisor.','2025-11-24 21:08:24','2025-11-24 21:08:24',NULL,NULL,287,NULL,NULL,NULL,2),(290,'step',NULL,'Active','Work Execution and Monitoring','Execution of work under permit with monitoring of conditions and compliance with permit requirements.',NULL,NULL,'Execute: work per permit, monitor conditions, verify controls maintained, report any changes. Monitor: work progress, conditions, compliance. Document: work progress, any issues.','2025-11-24 21:08:24','2025-11-24 21:08:24',NULL,NULL,287,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(291,'step',NULL,'Active','Permit Closure and Handback','Closure of permit after work completion including verification of work completion, removal of isolations, and area handback.',NULL,NULL,'Close: verify work complete, remove isolations, restore area, verify 