cal batches including assay, impurities, dose uniformity, and stability testing.',NULL,NULL,'Test: per specifications, using validated methods, document results. Include: assay, impurities, dose uniformity, particle size, microbial limits. Release: only if all tests pass.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,297,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(301,'step',NULL,'Active','Clinical Batch Release','Release of clinical batches by Qualified Person for use in clinical trials.',NULL,NULL,'Release: by QP (EU) or authorized person (US), after all requirements met. Document: release certificate, batch record review, test results review. Release to: clinical supply chain.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,297,NULL,NULL,NULL,4),(302,'process',NULL,'Active','Clinical Site Supply and Distribution','Management of clinical trial material supply to investigational sites including inventory management, shipment planning, distribution, and site inventory tracking.',NULL,NULL,'Supply: investigational product, comparator (if applicable), placebo (if applicable). Track: inventory at sites, shipments, returns, destruction. Maintain: distribution records, temperature records (if applicable).','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-12-08 18:11:14',NULL,NULL,356,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(303,'step',NULL,'Active','Site Inventory Planning','Planning of clinical site inventory including initial supply quantities, resupply planning, and inventory optimization.',NULL,NULL,'Plan: initial supply (based on enrollment projections), resupply triggers, inventory levels, expiry management. Optimize: inventory levels, minimize waste, ensure availability.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,302,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(304,'step',NULL,'Active','Clinical Material Shipment','Shipment of clinical trial materials to investigational sites including packaging, labeling, documentation, and tracking.',NULL,NULL,'Ship: per shipment plan, with proper packaging, correct labeling, complete documentation, temperature monitoring (if applicable). Track: shipment status, delivery, temperature.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,302,NULL,NULL,NULL,2),(305,'step',NULL,'Active','Site Inventory Management','Management of clinical trial material inventory at investigational sites including receipt, storage, dispensing, and returns.',NULL,NULL,'Manage: site inventory, receipt verification, storage conditions, dispensing records, returns processing. Monitor: inventory levels, expiry dates, storage conditions.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,302,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(306,'step',NULL,'Active','Material Returns and Destruction','Management of returned clinical trial materials including receipt, verification, and destruction.',NULL,NULL,'Return: unused product, expired product, damaged product. Verify: returned material, document returns, arrange destruction. Destroy: per protocol, with proper documentation, by authorized contractor.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,302,NULL,NULL,NULL,4),(307,'process',NULL,'Active','Trial Material Accountability','Complete accountability system for clinical trial materials including receipt, storage, dispensing, returns, and destruction tracking.',NULL,NULL,'Accountability: 100% accountability required. Track: every unit from receipt to destruction. Document: all transactions, maintain accountability records, reconcile inventory. Required for: regulatory inspection, trial integrity.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-12-08 18:11:14',NULL,NULL,356,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(308,'step',NULL,'Active','Material Receipt and Documentation','Receipt and documentation of clinical trial materials including verification, inventory entry, and storage assignment.',NULL,NULL,'Receive: verify shipment, check documentation, verify quantities, enter into inventory system, assign storage location. Document: receipt date, quantities, batch numbers, storage location.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,307,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(309,'step',NULL,'Active','Dispensing and Patient Assignment','Dispensing of clinical trial materials to patients including randomization, blinding, and dispensing documentation.',NULL,NULL,'Dispense: per randomization schedule, maintain blinding, document dispensing, assign to patient. Document: patient number, kit number, dispensing date, quantity dispensed, investigator signature.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,307,NULL,NULL,NULL,2),(310,'step',NULL,'Active','Accountability Reconciliation','Regular reconciliation of clinical trial material accountability including inventory counts and discrepancy investigation.',NULL,NULL,'Reconcile: regularly (monthly), count inventory, compare with records, investigate discrepancies, document reconciliation. Ensure: 100% accountability, all units accounted for.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,307,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(311,'step',NULL,'Active','Final Accountability Report','Final accountability report at trial end including summary of all material transactions and final reconciliation.',NULL,NULL,'Report: all receipts, dispensings, returns, destruction, final inventory, reconciliation. Document: complete accountability, any discrepancies, final status. Required for: regulatory submission, inspection.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-11-24 21:08:38',NULL,NULL,307,NULL,NULL,NULL,4),(312,'process',NULL,'Active','Patient Randomization and Blinding','Management of patient randomization and blinding procedures including randomization schedule generation, kit assignment, and unblinding procedures.',NULL,NULL,'Randomization: ensures treatment groups balanced, prevents selection bias. Blinding: prevents bias in treatment assignment and assessment. Maintain: blinding integrity, unblinding procedures for emergencies.','2025-11-24 21:08:38','2025-12-08 18:11:14',NULL,NULL,356,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(313,'step',NULL,'Active','Randomization Schedule Generation','Generation of