issions exceeding regulatory limits leading to environmental permit violations and regulatory action.',18,91,'Audit','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Manufacturing','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(19,'ENV-002','API Residues in Wastewater','Risk of API residues in wastewater exceeding discharge limits leading to environmental contamination and permit violations.',18,92,'HAZOP','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Manufacturing','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(20,'ENV-003','Hazardous Waste Disposal Non-Compliance','Risk of hazardous waste disposal non-compliance leading to environmental violations and regulatory penalties.',18,93,'Audit','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'All Stages','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(21,'OHS-001','Occupational Exposure to Potent APIs','Risk of occupational exposure to potent APIs during manufacturing leading to worker health hazards and OEL exceedances.',19,104,'HAZOP','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Manufacturing','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(22,'OHS-002','Pressurized System Failure and Explosion','Risk of pressurized system failures in propellant handling leading to explosions and worker injuries.',19,106,'HAZOP','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Manufacturing','MDI',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(23,'OHS-003','Fire and Explosion Hazards in Solvent Areas','Risk of fire and explosion hazards in solvent storage and handling areas leading to catastrophic incidents.',19,114,'HAZOP','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Manufacturing','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(24,'ENG-001','Energy Cost V