it Risk','Risk of product liability lawsuits due to product defects or patient harm leading to legal costs and damages.',24,176,'Management Review','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'Commercial','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(37,'LEG-002','Patent Infringement Claims','Risk of patent infringement claims leading to litigation, licensing costs, and product restrictions.',24,177,'Management Review','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'R&D','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(38,'LEG-003','Employment Law Violations','Risk of employment law violations leading to legal disputes, penalties, and workforce issues.',24,178,'Audit','2025-11-25',1,NULL,'All Stages','All',NULL,'Active','Medium','Quarterly',NULL,'Draft',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:19:05','2025-11-25 06:19:05',NULL),(84,'EHS-001','Chemical Spill Risk','Risk of chemical spills during material handling operations. Potential for environmental contamination and worker exposure to hazardous substances.',363,363,'Incident','2024-02-10',2,2,'Manufacturing','All Products','Warehouse Area','Active','High','Quarterly','2024-05-10','Approved',1,'2024-02-15',1,NULL,'2025-12-03 21:07:20','2025-12-03 21:07:20',2),(85,'EHS-002','Worker Safety Risk - Confined Spaces','Risk of accidents during maintenance activities in confined spaces. Inadequate safety procedures could lead to serious injury or fatality.',364,364,'Change Control','2024-03-15',2,2,'Manufacturing','All Products','Maintenance Areas','Active','High','Quarterly','2024-06-15','Approved',3,'2024-03-20',1,NULL,'2025-12-03 21:07:20','2025-12-03 21:07:20',2);
